<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Hummanites and Social Sciences</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fredoka:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    html, body {
      height: 100%;
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      overflow-y: auto;
    }

    .background {
      background: url("Strands-bg.png") no-repeat center center fixed;
      background-size: cover;
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0;
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 15px;
      padding: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #b075f0, #669eff);
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .logo {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 50%;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }
    .logo:hover { transform: scale(1.1); }

    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; }

    .content {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 30px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      min-height: 80vh; /* Extend content height for scrollbar */    
    }

    .strands {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 300px;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      text-align: left;
    }

    .strands h2 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 15px; }
    .strands h3 { font-size: 3rem; margin: 15px 0; }
    .strands p { font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    /* Accordion */
    .accordion {
      margin: 15px 0;
      border-radius: 15px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    }

    .accordion-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      transition: 0.3s;
    }
    .accordion-header:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    }

    .accordion-header span {
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    .accordion-header.active span {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }

    .accordion-content {
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height 0.4s ease, padding 0.4s ease;
      padding: 0 30px;
    }
    .accordion-content.open {
      max-height: 800px; /* enough for content */
      padding: 15px 30px;
    }

   .accordion-content.jobs-careers.open {
  max-height: none;
  overflow-y: visible;
  padding: 15px 20px;
}

    ul { margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 400; }
    ul li { margin: 5px 0; font-weight: 500; }

    footer { margin: 30px 0; }
    .home-btn {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #478ae8, #185a9d);
      border: none;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif;
      color: white;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }
    .home-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="background"></div>

  <header class="header">
    <img src="career-icon.png" alt="Logo" class="logo" onclick="window.location.href='result.html'">
    <h1>Associated Strands and Career</h1>
  </header>

  <main class="content">
    <section class="strands">
      <h3>SCIENCE TECHNOLOGY ENGINEERING MATHEMATICS (STEM)</h3>
      <p>
        This strand focuses on subjects like mathematics, physics, chemistry, and biology, 
        which are foundational for careers in science and technology.
      </p>

      <!-- Accordion 1 -->
      <div class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-header" onclick="toggleAccordion(this)">
          <h4>What You Will Study?</h4>
          <span>▶</span>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-content">
          <ul>
            <li><strong><u>Science:</u></strong> Biology, chemistry, physics, and environmental science.</li>
            <li><strong>Technology:</strong> Information technology, computer science, and digital literacy.</li>
            <li><strong>Engineering:</strong> Principles of engineering, design thinking, and problem-solving.</li>
            <li><strong>Mathematics:</strong> Advanced mathematics, statistics, and data analysis.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Accordion 2 -->
      <div class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-header" onclick="toggleAccordion(this)">
          <h4>Key Skills You Will Develop</h4>
          <span>▶</span>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-content">
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Problem-solving:</strong> Students learn to approach complex issues methodically and develop effective solutions.</li>
            <li><strong>Critical Thinking:</strong> Students learn to analyze information and different perspectives on human behavior and society.</li>
            <li><strong>Empathy and Social Awareness:</strong> The strand fosters an understanding of diverse cultures and societal challenges.</li>
            <li><strong>Research Skills:</strong> Students develop the ability to conduct inquiries into social phenomena.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Accordion 3 -->
      </div>
        <div class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-header" onclick="toggleAccordion(this)">
          <h4>Jobs And Careers</h4>
          <span>▶</span>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-content jobs-careers">
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Criminologist:</strong> studies the nature and causes of crime, analyzing crime patterns and social factors.</li>
           <center>
            <img  src="clipart (humss)/criminologist.jpg" alt="A sample image">
          </center>
            <li><strong>Journalism:</strong> Involves researching, writing, and reporting news and information.</li>
            <center>
            <img  src="clipart (humss)/journalist.png"alt="A sample image">
          </center>
            <li><strong>Communication:</strong> Professionals in this field work to convey information effectively across various media.</li>
             <center>
            <img  src="clipart (humss)/commu.png"alt="A sample image">
          </center>
            <li><strong>Teaching:</strong> Educators play a crucial role in shaping the minds of future generations.</li>
            <center>
              <img src="clipart (humss)/teaching.png"alt="A sample image">
            </center>
            <li><strong>Psychology:</strong> The study of the mind and behavior, with applications in various fields.</li>
            <center>
              <img src="clipart (humss)/psychology.png" width="600" height="300" alt="Sample Image">
              </center>
            <li><strong>Law:</strong> Legal professionals advocate for justice and represent clients in legal matters.</li>
            <center>
              <img src="clipart (humss)/law.png"alt="A sample image">
            </center>
            <li><strong>Public Relations:</strong> Involves managing communication between organizations and the public.</li>
            <center>
              <img src="clipart (humss)/public_relation-removebg-preview.png" width="600" height="300" alt="A sample image">
            </center>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <button class="home-btn" onclick="window.location.href='Homepage.html'">Back to Home</button>
  </footer>

  <script>
    function toggleAccordion(header) {
      const content = header.nextElementSibling;
      const arrow = header.querySelector("span");

      header.classList.toggle("active");
      content.classList.toggle("open");
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
